cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CV

The paper discusses the training of deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). However, since the paper focuses on the optimization of the training process using an evolutionary algorithm, cs.NE and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The use of RBMs and deep neural networks also suggests cs.AI and cs.CV as possible sub-categories. Finally, the mention of high-dimensional problems and optimization methods points towards cs.DS as a possible sub-category.
